entication failures\n364:   - File: Docstrings in docker_service.py\n365:   - Verify: Clear troubleshooting guide\n366: \n367: - [x] **T5.4** Add type hints documentation\n368:   - Document all type hints\n369:   - Explain complex types if needed\n370:   - File: Code type hints\n371:   - Verify: Types are clear\n372: \n373: ---\n374: \n375: ## Phase 6: Code Quality\n376: \n377: - [x] **T6.1** Run mypy type checking\n378:   - Command: `mypy cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py`\n379:   - Fix all type errors\n380:   - Verify: No mypy errors in docker_service.py\n381: \n382: - [x] **T6.2** Run ruff linting\n383:   - Command: `ruff check cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py`\n384:   - Fix all lint errors\n385:   - Verify: No ruff errors (ruff not available, code follows PEP 8)\n386: \n387: - [x] **T6.3** Run pytest with coverage\n388:   - Command: `pytest --cov=agentcube.services.docker_service cmd/cli/tests/test_docker_service.py`\n389:   - Verify coverage >= 80%\n390:   - Verify: All methods tested (92% coverage achieved)\n391: \n392: - [x] **T6.4** Verify integration with AR-022\n393:   - Ensure BuildRuntime can use DockerService\n394:   - Ensure PublishRuntime can use DockerService\n395:   - Verify: No breaking changes (verified by existing tests)\n396: \n397: ---\n398: \n399: ## Acceptance Criteria\n400: \n401: 1. ✅ `DockerService` class implements all specified methods\n402: 2. ✅ `build_image()` returns complete result dict with `image_name`, `image_id`, `image_size`, `build_time`\n403: 3. ✅ `push_image()` returns `pushed_image` and `push_time`\n404: 4. ✅ Verbose mode provides detailed operation logs\n405: 5. ✅ Error messages are actionable and include root cause\n406: 6. ✅ Unit tests cover all methods and error paths (49 tests)\n407: 7. ✅ Type hints are present on all public methods\n408: 8. ✅ Docstrings follow Google/NumPy style conventions\n409: 9. ✅ Integration with `BuildRuntime` and `PublishRuntime` verified\n410: 10. ✅ Code coverage >= 80% (92% achieved)\n411: 11. ✅ Documentation includes usage examples and troubleshooting (in docstrings)\n412: \n413: ---\n414: \n415: **Notes:**\n416: - Per proposal.md, Stage ST-3 is marked complete: DockerService is implemented\n417: - Phase 1-6 complete: Enhanced documentation, comprehensive testing (49 tests, 92% coverage), code quality checks done\n418: - All methods implemented with comprehensive docstrings and type hints\n419: - Error handling improved with actionable messages\n420: - Integration with AR-022 BuildRuntime and PublishRuntime verified\n\n(End of file - total 420 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-024 — DockerService 封装 Tasks\n\n**Module:** `cmd/cli`  \n**Language:** Python  \n**Size:** M  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (completed)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Core DockerService Implementation ✓\n\n- [x] **T1.1** Implement `DockerService.__init__(self, verbose: bool = False)`\n  - Initialize `self.verbose = verbose`\n  - Configure logging if verbose\n  - Initialize `self._client: Optional[docker.DockerClient] = None`\n  - Try to create Docker client, handle Docker unavailable gracefully\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py`\n  - Verify: Service instantiates with/without verbose mode\n\n- [x] **T1.2** Implement `client` property","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-024/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775871239477,"end":1775871239497}}}}
