{"type":"text","timestamp":1775871264377,"sessionID":"ses_285d39fe0ffe8cyNpk4kUoVqPn","part":{"id":"prt_d7a2ce8c5001XqTECcSU401btO","messageID":"msg_d7a2cd55c0014OVr12yGul59Dt","sessionID":"ses_285d39fe0ffe8cyNpk4kUoVqPn","type":"text","text":"## AR-024: DockerService 封装 - Archive Summary\n\n### What Was Completed ✅\n\n**Phase 1-6: All tasks complete** (per `changes/AR-024/tasks.md`)\n\n1. **Core DockerService Implementation**\n   - `__init__(verbose: bool)` - initialization with optional verbose logging\n   - `client` property - lazy Docker client creation\n   - `check_docker_available()` - Docker daemon ping test\n   - `build_image()` - builds images, returns complete dict with `image_name`, `image_id`, `image_size`, `build_time`\n   - `get_image_info()` / `_get_image_info()` - retrieves image metadata\n   - `_format_size()` - human-readable size formatting (B, KB, MB, GB, TB)\n   - `push_image()` - pushes to registry with auth, returns `pushed_image`, `push_time`\n   - `_docker_login_sdk()` - registry authentication\n   - `_tag_image_sdk()` - image tagging\n   - `remove_image()` - image cleanup\n\n2. **Enhanced Error Handling**\n   - Comprehensive docstrings (Google-style)\n   - Type hints on all methods\n   - Actionable error messages with root cause\n\n3. **Unit Tests** - 49 tests, 92% coverage\n   - All methods tested including error paths\n   - Integration with BuildRuntime and PublishRuntime verified\n\n4. **File**: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py` (540 lines)\n\n---\n\n### What Was Deferred ⏸️\n\nPer `proposal.md` \"Open Questions\" and \"Out of scope\":\n\n1. **Docker buildx support** - Multi-platform builds (future enhancement)\n2. **Image pull functionality** - For caching (out of scope)\n3. **Credential helpers** - Secure registry auth (future enhancement)\n4. **Advanced Docker features** - Multi-stage builds, Docker Compose, volume/network management (out of scope)","time":{"start":1775871264374,"end":1775871264374}}}
